---
import InnerLayout from '../layouts/InnerLayout.astro';
const canonicalURL = new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site);
---

<InnerLayout
  meta={{
    title: "Accessibility Statement for Frank Stallone's personal website",
    description:
      'For the last two decades, I have helped businesses of all sizes craft compelling user experiences that drove 100M+ in revenue.',
    canonicalURL: canonicalURL.href,
  }}
>
  <section class="region flow wrapper" id="main">
    <p>This is an accessibility statement from Frank Stallone.</p>

    <h2>Measures to support accessibility</h2>
    <p>
      Frank Stallone takes the following measures to ensure accessibility of
      Frank Stallone's personal website:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Include accessibility as part of our mission statement.</li>
      <li>Include accessibility throughout our internal policies.</li>
      <li>Integrate accessibility into our procurement practices.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Conformance status</h2>
    <p>
      The <a
        href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/standards-guidelines/wcag/"
        target="_blank">Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG)</a
      > defines requirements for designers and developers to improve accessibility
      for people with disabilities. It defines three levels of conformance: Level
      A, Level AA, and Level AAA. Frank Stallone's personal website is fully conformant
      with WCAG 2.1 level AA. Fully conformant means that the content fully conforms
      to the accessibility standard without any exceptions.
    </p>

    <h2>Additional accessibility considerations</h2>
    <p>
      I have also applied some Level AAA Success criteria. Colors have higher
      contrast ratios.
    </p>

    <h2>Feedback</h2>
    <p>
      I welcome your feedback on the accessibility of Frank Stallone's personal
      website. Please let us know if you encounter accessibility barriers on
      Frank Stallone's personal website <a href="#contact"
        >fill out my contact form</a
      >. I try to respond to feedback within 5 business days.
    </p>

    <h2>Technical specifications</h2>
    <p>
      Accessibility of Frank Stallone's personal website relies on the following
      technologies to work with the particular combination of web browser and
      any assistive technologies or plugins installed on your computer:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>HTML</li>
      <li>WAI-ARIA</li>
      <li>CSS</li>
      <li>JavaScript</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      These technologies are relied upon for conformance with the accessibility
      standards used.
    </p>

    <h2>Assessment approach</h2>
    <p>
      Frank Stallone assessed the accessibility of Frank Stallone's personal
      website by the following approaches:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Self-evaluation</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Date</h2>
    <p>
      This statement was created on 12 March 2024 using the W3C Accessibility
      Statement Generator Tool.
    </p>
  </section>
</InnerLayout>
